                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-base font-bold mb-3 text-gray-900">
              Poweragent AI
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed text-base">
              I led the full product development from initial concept through to pilot launch. We built a mobile-first experience using Twilio Voice for call handling and Whisper for real-time transcription.
            </p>
            <div class="space-y-2">
              <a href="https://www.producthunt.com/products/poweragent-ai" target="_blank" class="text-base font-medium text-gray-900 hover:text-gray-600 transition-colors">PowerAgent AI - Product Hunt</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Project 2: Ontario Community Energy Savings -->
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="aspect-[4/3] bg-gray-100 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden relative group">
            <img 
              src="/ecobee-products.png" 
              alt="Community Energy Savings" 
              class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-all duration-200 group-hover:blur-[2px]"
